    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine BMW E46 M3, a definitive driver\u2019s machine featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example is mechanically flawless; the Double-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rod bearings\u2014a critical maintenance item\u2014have been addressed with documented tolerance checks. The ZF 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, notch-free engagement, paired with a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains structurally superior with a reinforced rear subframe, while the suspension retains its original kinematic integrity. This is a collector-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance and a clean borescope report on all cylinders.",
